public class ProjectsManagedReference extends Reference implements Serializable
This is a reference, which is a view of a relationships from the perspective of one of the ends. A relationships is the link between 2 OMAS entities. A reference is used when working with OMAS entity APIs. An OMAS entity has attributes, classifications and references. This Reference is called ProjectsManagedReference. It is used in type ProjectManager to represent a reference to an OMAS entity of type project. The reference also contains information about the relationships; the relationships guid, name, relationships attributes and a list of unique attributes. Relationship attributes are attributes of the relationships. It is possible to work with the relationships itself using the OMAS API using the relationships guid contained in this reference.
